<div class="display-inline-block"><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer text-no-underline bg-transparent border-0 padding-0 text-left margin-0 text-normal text-primary" aria-controls="journal_context_menu">Bioinformatics</button></div>. 2012 Oct 12;28(24):3248–3256. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/bts580" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1093/bioinformatics/bts580</a>
</div>
<nav id="journal_context_menu" hidden="hidden"><ul class="menu-list font-family-ui" role="menu">
<li role="presentation"><a href='https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/search/?term="Bioinformatics"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem">Search in PMC</a></li>
<li role="presentation"><a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Bioinformatics"[jour]' lang="en" class="usa-link" role="menuitem">Search in PubMed</a></li>
